{"tid":1196364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人無撚得救","createTime":"2019-06-09T19:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T05:30:45.000Z","uid":67928,"like":529,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcb6b81aec6becf253cbddfddf1b10249af7ac0","tid":1196364,"uid":67928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:08:10.000Z","msg":"今日遊行過 衝擊過<br />\n其實仲有人係出面衝緊<br />\n為既係守護我地既香港<br />\n<br />\n眼見衝擊立會既時候<br />\n仲有一大群人係斜路揸住個電話影影影<br />\n下面明明已經開咗個頭 <br />\n屌咗幾百次都唔肯落黎幫下我<br />\n你可以係後面捉實我地既人 <br />\n咁已經幫到好大既忙 <br />\n<br />\n成群男人高高大大 匿係後面做縮頭烏龜<br />\n一個女子都無野驚 仲要保護你地？<br />\n仲未計群黑警賣港賊 <br />\n<br />\n一百萬人遊行 <br />\n一半人留低都打撚死班狗<br />\n夜晚得個幾百人 又無組織無部署<br />\n成班人仲可以冷眼旁觀 <br />\n<br />\n香港人唔撚值得我地救"},{"pid":"598ea0b51037af73aa83230fe6dd288559738f4b","tid":1196364,"uid":431,"like":264,"dislike":3,"score":261,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:09:25.000Z","msg":"日唞去完遊行post ig打個卡夜晚返屋企打開電視睇新聞話唔好衝大家係和平表達意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲戇鳩仔到底幾撚時先死"},{"pid":"67f8284d975feadafde7ce64a6209a9a0828f4bf","tid":1196364,"uid":194177,"like":70,"dislike":3,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"香港人對你地唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b5e7f73d4bca186553019b84caeee4df293c63","tid":1196364,"uid":26773,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:10:05.000Z","msg":"一哥都講左<br />\n入面無人衝黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00fd12fc1cf96dbcaad8b7a7bd7a20ed67586f4","tid":1196364,"uid":61372,"like":116,"dislike":3,"score":113,"quote":{"pid":"c9b5e7f73d4bca186553019b84caeee4df293c63","tid":1196364,"uid":26773,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:10:05.000Z","msg":"一哥都講左